{"tid":733600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"艾美琦呻拍AV遭壓價","createTime":"2018-07-08T01:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T06:31:51.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"510b2d8f962efe82892918a139a0f2d0cd247b62","tid":733600,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180708/large/08ec4p16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180708%2Flarge%2F08ec4p16.jpg&h=c1641f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n艾美琦（右）與中日混血兒多香子昨日到旺角行人專用區宣傳即將推出的寫真，兩人大玩意淫遊戲，又當眾除衫露出性感bra top。她們互餵香蕉時，多香子更疑似露暈，又把香蕉放在乳溝中間，吸引大批男士圍觀。早前兩人在日本以20萬拍攝6部AV，艾美琦透露稍後將再到日本拍AV：「𠵱家傾緊價錢，對方想壓價，起碼要同價先會再拍。」她又指契媽黃夏蕙沒有因為她拍AV生氣：「原來佢好開通。」"},{"pid":"1d04803de6366b56f0635b9ba4b9fd7764482c13","tid":733600,"uid":182334,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"同一招要用幾多次？拍左先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afeb2d4c17e2f5e7a5318b67c37b0ee8dda99f8d","tid":733600,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf62dd507cc6c3d1b0e795be532cf0f5b803257","tid":733600,"uid":82450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰喎"},{"pid":"014e93839f8160fde9c4f6fec4cb824a61c07589","tid":733600,"uid":193352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2494a0ac49c3c2dac2bf9537cf8f361bdb2c51fc","tid":733600,"uid":196310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:31:51.000Z","msg":"又吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}